Extreme sports:
skateboarding 滑板运动

skydiving 空中跳伞

downhill skiing 滑降滑雪

rock climbing 攀岩

surfing

snowboarding 滑雪

hang gliding 乘风滑翔，悬挂式滑翔

powerboat racing 赛艇

white-water rafting 白水漂流

windsurfing 帆板运动

parachute降落伞

leg straps 腿部肩带

harness 背带，马具

free fall 自由降落

wimp out受惊吓，失去勇气

feel invincible 感觉到无敌的

thrill-seeker 寻求刺激的人

sweat 流汗

transfixed 惊讶，惊呆

debilitating 非常虚弱的

Idioms:
by a long shot(by a great deal or amount)

show someone up(make someone look bad)

on top of that(also, or additionally)

strike me(appear, or seem like)

never hear the end of it(people will talk about it for a long time)

look forward to


